Today's #decluttering mission, for May 17th, is to continue to #declutter your current filing cabinet, file box, binders, or wherever in the past you've held #papers, to remove those which are no longer important or relevant. Here's the article on how to do this, which we also used yesterday: http://www.home-storage-solutions-101.com/file-clutter.html (there's a clickable link in my profile)⠀
⠀⠀
Once you've worked on this mission I'd love to see your results, so be sure to use the #Declutter365 hashtag so I can find what you've done. ⠀⠀
